The technology is safe, similar solutions are used in parking garages, toll roads and mobile pay solutions.

When you enter our stations, a camera will read your license plate and activate the fuel pump next to your car, using the payment card you have entered in the app. You can choose if you want to approve each transaction by clicking once on your smartphone or if you want the process to be completely automatic.
